<br>
1) Pony - buy an entry level horse to get a basic movement speed upgrade and medding benefits.   (9kp-ish).<br>
<br>
2) Earring of Solstice - buy the &quot;gifts&quot; necessary to get the EoS and get the upgraded stats and FT1 benefit.  (9kp-ish).<br>
<br>
3) JBoot MQ - raw movement speed upgrade.  (5kp-ish).<br>
<br>
4) Resist Gear - all my gear to date has been purchased with INT, HP, and AC in mind, in short, currently my resists stink.<br>
<br>
5) Other?<br>
<br>
I am a casual player, not in a guild, mostly solo and/or play in small groups.  I am unlikely to do any regular raiding although I hope to go on  a raid or two along the way.  Getting the Mage Epic is probably not in the cards for me.<br>
<br>
Thanks. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=368916">Fenobleu Wayfarer</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
